team.description: We are like minded passionate people who belong to different technical backgrounds and create exciting projects and share their experiences with fellow developers. We provide a group to share different ideas and network with fellow developers. GDG Indore is a place to learn about Google technologies and development tools. We seek to provide intellectual grounding through tech sessions conducted throughout the year. We host a variety of technical activities for developers - from just a few people getting together to live stream Google events, to large gatherings with demos and tech talks, to hackathons. Our zeal to contribute to the development of society and passion for technology drives our community. Anyone with the same passion and interest can become our team member. It is open to and free for all interested.
